{"tid":2195454,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【柒到冇眼睇】邱騰華稱與澳洲商討旅遊氣泡　澳洲外交部否認","createTime":"2020-09-09T07:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T09:37:52.000Z","uid":6497,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"f85da1563a1bbc13e551c7791e6c324b41806b91","tid":2195454,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:47:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A8%B1%E8%88%87%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E5%95%86%E8%A8%8E%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E6%B0%A3%E6%B3%A1-%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%2595%2586%25E8%25A8%258E%25E6%2597%2585%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%25B3%25A1-%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%2F&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwgwzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=0daccc95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%2595%2586%25E8%25A8%258E%25E6%2597%2585%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%25B3%25A1-%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%2F&h=bfa22d60\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A8%B1%E8%88%87%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E5%95%86%E8%A8%8E%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E6%B0%A3%E6%B3%A1-%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20200909-0520copy_V0yUX_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20200909-0520copy_V0yUX_1200x0.png&h=baf593cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受全球武漢肺炎 (COVID-19) 疫情影響，全球客運運輸幾乎停頓，旅遊業也嚴重受創。商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華昨日（8 日）表示，港府正與 11 個國家和地區商討實施「旅遊氣泡」政策，逐步恢復旅遊往返，當中包括澳洲及紐西蘭。不過澳洲外交部今日否認邱騰華的說法，稱澳洲目前只有與紐西蘭商討相關措施。<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華昨日在記者招待會中指與 11 個國家商討旅遊氣泡政策，並已與日本和泰國政府展開雙邊接觸，以及委托了德國作為協調國，與歐盟多國討論旅遊出入境新安排。他指紐西蘭及澳洲同樣對此安排感興趣，唯需待澳紐兩國確立旅遊氣泡政策。<br />\n<br />\n不過澳洲外交部今日回應當地媒體 SBS 查詢時表示，現階段澳洲只會跟紐西蘭討論開放邊境政策。發言人強調，澳洲將會在安全時解封邊境，並指提否開放需基於衛生建議，要按部就班完成。<br />\n<br />\n根據澳洲旅遊指引網站 SmartTraveller 資料，該國依然禁止所有海外旅遊。網站同時指出香港社區傳播有增加趨勢，提醒旅客需保持社交距離以及戴上口罩。另外，該國較早前也曾建議前往當地的國民要小心誤觸《國安法》。"},{"pid":"11e1cfc08dbf530732718d0275387e2f68e1b9fd","tid":2195454,"uid":116289,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:48:21.000Z","msg":"張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f42a36fdd0ddef439f583ffd79bcec032fb2cdd","tid":2195454,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:49:54.000Z","msg":"泡泡吹出嚟架姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f0b9d65d6224fca6cabc6022312982ae73174ba","tid":2195454,"uid":13663,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:50:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NjGtec1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNjGtec1.jpg&h=fa77f469&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a43987272d8973689dc05c3efdc2c617ae07aad7","tid":2195454,"uid":238415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:52:33.000Z","msg":"港共: 對方否認唔代表無傾過"},{"pid":"295a8f6cf92a6febe8381b6b78df87375e6f856e","tid":2195454,"uid":268957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11e1cfc08dbf530732718d0275387e2f68e1b9fd","tid":2195454,"uid":116289,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T07:48:21.000Z","msg":"張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im